            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2 class="heading mb-4"><strong>A Message from Dr. Khaled & Dr. Mohammed Ghalwash</strong></h2>
                <p class="text-black" style="font-size: 17px;">Dear valued patients from afar,</p>

                <p class="text-black" style="font-size: 17px;"><strong>We extend our warmest welcome to you from the heart of Alexandria</strong>, where ancient wisdom meets modern medical excellence. As you consider your journey to our clinic, we want you to know that you're not just coming for a medical procedure – you're becoming part of our extended family.</p>

                <p class="text-black" style="font-size: 17px;">Our commitment goes beyond the operating room. We understand that traveling for medical care can feel daunting, which is why we've designed a comprehensive care program that embraces both your medical needs and your comfort as our guest in Alexandria.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
                <div class="service-card p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="mb-3"><strong>Your Medical Journey</strong></h3>
                    <p>From your first consultation to your final follow-up, we provide:</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>✓ Personalized treatment plans</li>
                        <li>✓ Virtual pre-consultation options</li>
                        <li>✓ Dedicated patient coordinator</li>
                        <li>✓ Comprehensive aftercare support</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
                <div class="service-card p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="mb-3"><strong>Experience Alexandria</strong></h3>
                    <p>During your recovery, immerse yourself in our city's rich heritage:</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>✓ Visit the historic Bibliotheca Alexandrina</li>
                        <li>✓ Stroll along the Mediterranean Corniche</li>
                        <li>✓ Explore ancient Roman theaters</li>
                        <li>✓ Taste authentic Egyptian cuisine</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8 text-center">
                <h3 class="mb-4"><strong>Let Us Guide Your Journey</strong></h3>
                <p class="mb-4">We invite you to explore our comprehensive support services designed specifically for our out-of-town patients:</p>

                <div class="row mt-4">
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <a href="/Out_of_town/Concierge_Services" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Concierge Services</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <a href="/Out_of_town/Hotels_Accommodations" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Accommodations</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <a href="/Out_of_town/Alexandria_Attractions" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">City Attractions</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{{> footer}}

</body>
</html>

